### NAAS — Payouts API manual tests

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@contentType = application/json
@token = PASTE_JWT_HERE
@groupId = PASTE_GROUP_ID_HERE
@payoutId = PASTE_PAYOUT_ID_HERE

### ──── List all payouts ─────────────────────────────────────────────

GET {{baseUrl}}/groups/{{groupId}}/payouts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ──── Current cycle payout status ─────────────────────────────────

GET {{baseUrl}}/groups/{{groupId}}/payouts/current
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ──── Nominate recipient (President Decides mode only) ─────────────

POST {{baseUrl}}/groups/{{groupId}}/payouts/nominate
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "recipientId": "PASTE_RECIPIENT_USER_ID"
}

### ──── Approve payout (President) ──────────────────────────────────

POST {{baseUrl}}/groups/{{groupId}}/payouts/{{payoutId}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ──── Execute payout (Treasurer) ──────────────────────────────────

POST {{baseUrl}}/groups/{{groupId}}/payouts/{{payoutId}}/execute
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
